{"tid":585960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范太：深圳上海跑得快，香港手腳在打架","createTime":"2018-03-09T06:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T08:25:33.000Z","uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"34021e0abf3548051c29f3a153f17b70c4f13039","tid":585960,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180309/s00001/5e35707aff384dc4bd5411df6c35c9d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180309%2Fs00001%2F5e35707aff384dc4bd5411df6c35c9d4.jpg&h=98b82371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第十二屆全國人大常委范徐麗泰接受《北京青年報》訪問時，談到香港和內地城市的發展互動，她說：「現在深圳、上海跑得很快，可我們香港『選手』手腳在相互打架。」對於有說法指「深圳的GDP超過香港」，范太認為這對香港是激勵。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰在訪問中指出，如果能加深香港與內地的了解，抓住「粵港澳大灣區」發展建設的契機，香港將重振「東方之珠」的榮光。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有說法稱「深圳GDP超越香港」，她怎麼看待外界拿深圳、香港等城市比較？范太說，過去5年，香港特區政府想要做些事情，包括立法、撥款等，會受到立法會內反對派議員阻礙，造成很多計劃一拖再拖，難以推進。范太覺得香港、深圳、上海、新加坡、東京這些城市，就像在同一個跑道上的「選手」，現在別人都努力地跑，「深圳、上海跑得很快，但香港『選手』的手和腳在相互打架，自然就跑不起來」。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰形容香港新一屆特區政府「積極有為」，希望上述的情況能得到改善。她又說，香港多的是聰明、勤勉的人才，願意投身到香港和內地發展建設。對於「深圳的GDP（本地生產總值）超過香港」的說法，她認為是對香港的激勵，香港要恭喜深圳，更要努力提升自己的實力，全力以赴追上去。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》記者翻查資料，早前有傳媒稱香港GDP去年達2.66萬億港元，深圳市GDP是2.24萬億元人民幣，換算後是2.68萬億港元，形容這是首次超過香港。不過深圳統計局本月初表示，按去年人民幣兌換港幣1.1552折算，香港GDP是2.3萬億元人民幣，深圳比香港仍差611億元人民幣（約754億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n(北京青年報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22db7b3e811f5c7d26d8affe5478a844a9f9d5af","tid":585960,"uid":41116,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"二千幾萬人口既城市gdp 超香港有咩奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b8f714c8691a9c40712e7e423d923eaad3c289","tid":585960,"uid":15815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"就係畀你班仆街搞到痙攣🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"a66a6a70769a7cace527ecc7e955c6ea3aedf44e","tid":585960,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁北京呢？？當自己係跑狗定人？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW，真GDP過左香港未？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0305e71d7d910711fb5fc8a3d82fc0655f8d7fdc","tid":585960,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"兩個城市加埋北京逼到pk，公只衛生仲停留係三十年前，唔知有咩好羨慕，不如范太你搬上去住啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fd78a8f74f8755aaffc0c196d0fd061c75056e","tid":585960,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"就係因為有呢d妖婦阻撚住晒"},{"pid":"107dda2126a6846dfb60c693a1872bb009906dce","tid":585960,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7258ea7c492eb47954f77d09438511a5561594","tid":585960,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"北韓都同美國建交喇，仲親中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed868fcc0ede27574cba4e0498251234621b7c5","tid":585960,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6ed19cb5998a28c33cd2a57a7ca6641ce45cc2c","tid":585960,"uid":84228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09